<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(لربحت)</span> <span class="c2">(٩)</span> <span class="c2">(مثل)</span> <span class="c2">(١٠)</span> عطاء الكوفة <span class="c2">(١١)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
